      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring a direct mechanical connection to the rear-mounted M-Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive double-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high torque loads. The suspension geometry is sharpened by refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, providing the precise turn-in and communicative feedback expected of this chassis. A true driver\u2019s specification that prioritizes power delivery and handling kinematics over cosmetic perfection.",
